===Noun===
'''ezel''' {{m}} (''plural:'' '''ezels''')
#A domestic animal, ''Equus asinus'', similar to a horse with long ears.
#An upright frame, usually on three legs, for displaying or supporting something, such as an artist's canvas.
#A foolish person.

